    "bio": "Zhenzhong Zeng is a Professor at the School of Environmental Science and Engineering, Southern University of Science and Technology. He is a Changjiang Distinguished Professor and his research focuses on earth system processes and global change. He has published 189+ papers including in Nature, Science, Nature Sustainability, Nature Climate Change, Nature Geoscience, and Nature Water.",
    "bioCn": "曾振中，南方科技大学环境科学与工程学院教授、长江学者特聘教授。研究方向为地球系统过程与全球变化，已在 Nature、Science、Nature Sustainability、Nature Climate Change、Nature Geoscience、Nature Water 等期刊发表论文189余篇。",
    "honors": [
